智衡权重确定平台 (Intelligent Weight Determination Platform)

本软件由厦门大学数据挖掘研究中心开发，用于大语言模型驱动的权重方法推荐。

This software was developed by Xiamen University Data-Mining Research Center 
for LLM-driven weight method recommendation.

